subSubSection.paragraph:
Ecology and bathymetric distribution. No macrosymbionts were observed on this sponge. The only specimen was collected from soft seabed with a mix of mud and carbonate sand, at 500 m depth ( Lavrado & Ignacio 2006 ;
Muricy et al. 2006
).
